# ── Decision Memory Engine (DME) — example environment ──────────────────────
# Copy this file to `.env`  (cp .env.example .env)  and fill in your own values.
# NEVER commit your real .env — it is git-ignored.

# Groq API key — powers the AI tabs (Deep Analysis, Safety & Bias, AI Assistant).
# Get a free key at https://console.groq.com/keys
GROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_api_key_here

# ── Notes ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# The app reads GROQ_API_KEY from the environment. Two ways to supply it:
#   1) Export it in your shell / put it in this .env, OR
#   2) Paste it into the API-key field in the app's sidebar at runtime.
# Without a key, the ML prediction and Decision Memory features still work —
# only the LLM-powered tabs are disabled (graceful degradation).
